OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Flight and patchy rain possible during
OL,7,Fthe evening, but this easing overnight
OL,8,Fwith clear spells developing. Clouding
OL,9,Fover again towards dawn. Becoming
OL,10,Fbreezy, especially on the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy this morning with
OL,13,Frain spreading eastwards, perhaps with
OL,14,Fthe odd heavier burst. Rain clearing
OL,15,Fthe east by mid-afternoon, leaving
OL,16,Fsunny spells. Isolated showers
OL,17,Fpossible later, these occasionally
OL,18,Fheavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
