OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunshine
OL,6,Fand showers Sunday and Monday, these
OL,7,Fpotentially heavy and thundery. Fewer
OL,8,Fshowers Tuesday but turning cloudy.
OL,9,FBreezy on Sunday, then easing.
OL,10,FTemperatures around average, but
OL,11,Fovernight frost is possible.
